title: Ebro In The Morning - Paul Wall Plays White-Ish Wednesday + Tory Lanez In Cuffs

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 4/6/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Tory Lanez arrest, a special fans birthday, and Paul Wall joins for White-Ish Wednesday!

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
